{
  "stem": "1141.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I went back this summer to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to look up these people, because I wanted to help them in any way I could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I was told not to go into town because of the political reasons, what went on there this summer, the separation from Slovak-- Slovensko from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't want to take a chance to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very dear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These Gentile friends, they were like my sisters and brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not know the difference between them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was not their fault that they turned against us, because as I've said before, they were afraid of their own life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, there were some people who deliberately waited to chase us out from our homes so they can take over.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they so-- they-- they succeeded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because when we left, we left with what we had on our backs, the clothes on our backs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was left behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gendarme-- this police-- came and they took him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took him into Poland, and it was a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took him to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only him, but the rest of the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not only from that town, but from all-- all over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when he came back, he was unrecognizable from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] He finally wound up in Auschwitz, in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, they were sneaking in food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever they-- they were able to exchange for food, they-- people would come in and take whatever was any-- of any value, and they brought food for that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943 they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave us 24 hours to clear out from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
